Package: batchcreator
Type: Package
Title: Create Balanced Wet-Lab Sample Batches and Tube Pick Lists
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      given = "Bradley",
      family = "Ward",
      email = "bradleyalexward@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Tool for creating balanced wet-lab batches from sample metadata,
    optionally matching selected samples to biobank inventory, generating
    tube pick lists, updating processing flags, and rendering PDF batch
    reports. The package is designed for omics workflows where sample
    selection needs to be reproducible, balanced across strata, and linked
    to physical inventory.
